{"tid":1590850,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"近7成球迷認同美斯 實至名歸！","createTime":"2019-09-24T02:28:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T07:48:52.000Z","uid":54373,"like":30,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"07cce70e8f108b83ef92bd9ebf40be1eef6ae42f","tid":1590850,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T02:28:09.000Z","msg":"多數球迷認可美斯獲獎<br />\n<br />\n  美斯擊敗了C.朗拿度和雲迪積克獲得了FIFA年度最佳球員獎，對於這一結果，西班牙媒體做了民意調查，多數球迷服氣美斯得獎。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">  在上個賽季，美斯49場比賽攻入51球，是西甲最佳射手、歐冠盃最佳射手和歐洲金靴的獲得者，另外他還有21次助攻，無疑是球壇最為亮眼的數據。</span><br />\n<br />\n  不過，也有人認為，雲迪積克才是最出色的球員，他穩健的發揮幫助利物浦奪得了歐冠盃冠軍，這一球會層面的最高榮譽。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n  那麼人們是否認可美斯獲獎呢？《馬卡報》對此進行了調查，根據球迷投票結果顯示，66%的球迷認為美斯配的上捧得獎項，他今年獲獎是實至名歸。"},{"pid":"228b4314ea162eab98f9f9c1d4389669db8a7188","tid":1590850,"uid":125724,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T02:30:11.000Z","msg":"牙朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f755aee6f613dc28f47b02d34abd24da215ec7d","tid":1590850,"uid":90515,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T02:34:53.000Z","msg":"連馬卡班皇迷都支持"},{"pid":"aa8c29de303ac3a3017eb575f5ec76814555a277","tid":1590850,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T02:39:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://img.fifa.com/image/upload/z0gygcuwnxuz6pimfuhm.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.fifa.com%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fz0gygcuwnxuz6pimfuhm.pdf&d=1Biu5Jcu4NfhTOeMSm0obmWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=35b9ba54\" target=\"_blank\">https://img.fifa.com/image/upload/z0gygcuwnxuz6pimfuhm.pdf</a><br />\n投票紀錄"},{"pid":"4076c5663c568a3459c6c7a3d135576fa9032c63","tid":1590850,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:54:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09acf6193c92a2daf0aaeaad863c48ee9196546c","tid":1590850,"uid":43785,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":